Add a spec for the nlctrl family.

Example usage:

./tools/net/ynl/cli.py \
    --spec Documentation/netlink/specs/nlctrl.yaml \
    --do getfamily --json '{"family-name": "nlctrl"}'

./tools/net/ynl/cli.py \
    --spec Documentation/netlink/specs/nlctrl.yaml \
    --dump getpolicy --json '{"family-name": "nlctrl"}'

